OL,3,CWarning of 'serious pest' beetle
OL,4,Cspotted in Wales
OL,6,FPeople are being advised to keep an
OL,7,Feye out for a "serious pest" that's
OL,8,Fbeen spotted in Wales.
OL,10,FWales' Chief Plant Health Officer has
OL,11,Fasked all landowners, foresters and
OL,12,Ffarmers to be vigilant for signs of a
OL,13,Fbeetle that poses a serious threat to
OL,14,Fspruce trees.
OL,16,FThe eight-toothed spruce bark beetle,
OL,17,Falso referred to as Ips typographus,
OL,18,Fhas been caught in surveillance traps
OL,19,Fin Monmouthshire.
