OL,4,Cspotted in Wales
OL,6,FHowever National Resources Wales has
OL,7,Fconfirmed following an investigation
OL,8,Fthat "there is no evidence of an
OL,9,Foutbreak in the area".
OL,11,FExperts have warned that if left
OL,12,Funcontrolled, the beetle has the
OL,13,Fpotential to cause significant damage
OL,14,Fto Britain's spruce-based forestry and
OL,15,Ftimber industries.
