OL,3,CWarning of 'serious pest' beetle
OL,4,Cspotted in Wales
OL,6,FThe beetle can bore through tree bark,
OL,7,Fcausing damage which makes it hard for
OL,8,Fthe tree to transport nutrients.
OL,9,FDespite preferring stressed or dying
OL,10,Ftrees, under the right conditions it
OL,11,Fcan attack healthy trees.
OL,13,FRecent findings in England have also
OL,14,Fshown the pest on Sitka spruce trees
OL,15,Fin the UK for the first time.
