OL,3,CWarning of 'serious pest' beetle
OL,4,Cspotted in Wales
OL,6,FDeputy First Minister with
OL,7,Fresponsibility for Climate Change, Huw
OL,8,FIrranca-Davies said: "Please remain
OL,9,Fvigilant for signs of the eight-
OL,10,Ftoothed spruce bark beetle (Ips
OL,11,Ftypographus) as it is considered a
OL,12,Fserious pest to spruce trees.
OL,14,F"If you think you have spotted signs
OL,15,Fof this beetle then please submit your
OL,16,Ffindings via the Tree Alert form."
OL,18,FThe Welsh Plant Health Surveillance
OL,19,FNetwork has established traps across
OL,20,FWales to help keep an eye on the
OL,21,Fhealth of the trees.
